Package frc.robot.subsystems

Class Climber

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.subsystems.Climber
  • public class Climber
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the code for the climber. It initializes motor controllers/pneumatics and has methods for various functions of the climber.

        public void setSpeedArm​(double speed)
        Sets the arm motor to a given speed. Note: this motor should only be run at a negative speed, since the arm's hook is pneumatically deployed upwards.
        Parameters:
        speed - the speed to run the arm at
